text: Theodore Brinckman may refer to: *Sir Theodore Brinckman, 1st Baronet (1798–1880), British MP for Yarmouth *Sir Theodore Brinckman, 2nd Baronet (1830–1905), his son, British Liberal MP for Canterbury *Sir Theodore Brinckman, 4th Baronet (1898–1954), British cricketer ==See also== *Brinckman (surname)
